OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScholz: Nuclear risk from  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FRussia has lessened        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The risk of nuclear weapons being used 
OL,6, in the Ukraine conflict has lessened   
OL,7, "for the time being", says German      
OL,8, Chancellor Olaf Scholz.                
OL,10,F"Russia has stopped threatening to use 
OL,11,Fnuclear weapons in response to the     
OL,12,Finternational community marking a red  
OL,13,Fline," Mr Scholz said.                 
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, Russia's Vladimir Putin  
OL,16,Fsuggested that Moscow would only use   
OL,17,Fnuclear weapons in retaliation.        
OL,19,FBut the US denounced the comments as   
OL,20,F"loose talk".                          
